product.name: Joosenhouse Modern LED Picture Lights 24.4 inch, Antique Bronze Metal Artwork Display Lamp with Rotatable Sconces Lamp Head, 14W (70W Eqv.), Hardwired Connection, 3000K Warm White 840Lm…
product.description:
Bronze LED Vanity Light
These vanity light fixtures add contemporary atmosphere to your living space with simple and modern styles.
Superb craftsmanship combined with modern style and innovative design creates these wonderful vanity lighting fixtures
which makes it a perfect decor for your bathroom ,dressing table, mirror cabinets, vanity table, art display etc.
product.bullet_points:
• Lighting Direction Adjustable Over Pictures: The picture light’s arm and light's tube (24.4 inches) can be rotated UP and DOWN 180° to adjust the lighting direction to your desired position
• Premium Quality: Full metal construction for outstanding durability; Antique bronze electro-painting process ensures reliable surface finishing color and safe usage. Low heat emission best preserves your artwork throughout its long service life
• Single Arm Design Lighting Fixture: Single metal swing arm design to ensure the wall sconce looks more modern. This will be one perfect unique swing arm wall lamp for paintings in bedroom bedside, bathroom, indoor house, farmhouse
• 110V working voltage: This art lights for paintings is with 100-120V AC working voltage, NOT BATTERY OPERATED. Hard-wired connection to 110V AC power; NON-DIMMABLE
• Easy Installation & Multipurpose: Very easy to wall mounted with provided screws. Good choice for lighting up your paintings, artworks, pictures, mirror, dart board, photos, etc. It can be also used as a desk light bar for desk against a wall or other accent scone lamps
